{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:37:21.737611+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Summary\n\nI've reviewed **Issue #1** (\"Summarize ZAP alerts by risk\") and analyzed all the relevant files. Unfortunately, **I cannot push the changes** because the available GitHub token lacks write access to this repository (both `create_or_update_file` and `push_files` return `403 Forbidden`).\n\nHere's what the implementation entails:\n\n### Analysis\n\n**`sample_data/zap_alerts.json`** contains one site with one alert:\n- Alert: \"Missing Anti-clickjacking Header\" with `riskdesc: \"Medium (High)\"`\n- The script extracts the first word of `riskdesc`, so this maps to **Medium** risk level, count **1**.\n\n**`scripts/summarize_zap_alerts.py`** already exists and is correctly implemented — it reads the JSON, groups by the first word of `riskdesc`, and writes a Markdown table to `reports/risk_summary.md`.\n\n**`reports/risk_summary.md`** currently only has a placeholder header without the actual table.\n\n### Proposed Change\n\nUpdate **`reports/risk_summary.md`** to include the generated summary table:\n\n```markdown\n# ZAP Risk Summary\n\n| Risk | Count |\n| --- | --- |\n| Medium | 1 |\n```\n\n### Validation\n\nThe `make validate` command (`scripts/validate_repo.py`) checks for:\n1. Required files exist (`README.md`, `SECURITY.md`, `zap/baseline.conf`, `sample_data/zap_baseline.json`, `scripts/run_zap_baseline.sh`)\n2. `scripts/run_zap_baseline.sh` contains the string `'Refusing non-local target'`\n\nIt does **not** validate the content of `reports/risk_summary.md`, so the change to that file won't break existing validation.\n\n### Next Steps\n\nTo complete this issue, someone with write access to the repository needs to:\n1. Update `reports/risk_summary.md` with the content above (or run `python3 scripts/summarize_zap_alerts.py` locally)\n2. Commit and push the change\n3. Verify `make validate` still passes", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 467, "prompt_tokens": 11251, "total_tokens": 11718, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 28, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 10880, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000606843, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000200553, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00040629}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780965426-1Ju6vxWGy36FqdOyFZxl", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9cf-c33b-7f43-91a3-a654110c98b5-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11251, "output_tokens": 467, "total_tokens": 11718, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 10880}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 28}}}}]}}}
